rental.headline: Bright two bedroom apartment
rental.description:
Within a beautifully maintained smaller block, this delightful renovated two bedroom apartment features floorboards through living areas and eat in kitchen and is recently painted throughout, it has an abundance of natural light and all rooms and the bathroom are naturally ventilated.
Located on the top level of the building it sits high with a leafy outlook. It is both quiet and incredibly convenient.
There is a secure lock up garage, and quaint balcony with lovely aspect.
Situated across the road from Coles, Chemist Wharehouse, cafes and other Turramurra Shops, and stones throw to Turramurra Station and extensive bus network it simply could not be more conveniently located.

rental.headline: Exquisitely Presented, Picture Perfect | (3 Month Lease)
rental.description:
This is a beautiful family home which has been meticulously maintained and artfully modernised for contemporary living. With a masterful layout and picture perfect landscape.
The entry opens to a wide, marble tiled foyer which separates the living and bedroom wings of the home. Along the right side a gracious formal lounge room overlooks the North West facing garden. Bright and spacious, it features a gas fireplace with built in bookcases on either side.
From the dining room a large family room, with air conditioner and gas heating, overlooks a level, private garden. Mature camellias and viburnum frame the garden with depth added by mature trees in neighbouring gardens.
The kitchen, recently upgraded, has an ideal layout with excellent storage and includes; Smeg cook top and oven, granite bench tops, pantry and wall mounted flat screen TV. A bright, cheerful sun room overlooks the backyard.
There are four spacious bedrooms. The master bedroom overlooks the garden and includes a modern ensuite. The bright, airy fourth bedroom/guest room is downstairs with secure, private entry and would also suit use as a home office.
Set in park like, landscaped grounds, handsome mature shrubs frame the outlook from every room. The gentle undulating slope providing a park like vista.
Conveniently located near St Ives Village, premier government and private schools and easy access to both train and bus lines.
Available only for a term of three months.

residential.headline: Top Spot Apartment with Private Rooftop Space and Expansive Terrace
residential.description:
This apartment was the display apartment for this highly successful development,Twin Peaks.
Three car spaces plus generous storage! One of a kind!
With prized North East aspect, this apartment offers the space and privacy of a home with the security and convenience of apartment living. It's also unique for it's exclusive use of the rooftop area with 2 terraces and views
Once inside the apartment feels light and spacious, enhanced by lofty 2.75M approx. high ceilings. Beautifully framed by white plantation shutters, the living and dining area extend seamlessly to the private outdoor terrace and captures a pleasant outlook.
Featuring a gourmet kitchen with gas and stainless steel appliances, it is a perfect size with ample storage.
There are two large bedrooms one with an ensuite and each have built in wardrobes.
It has exclusive use of a completely separated rooftop storage space with bathroom and air conditionining plus an enormous terrace with fantastic views that overlooks Barker College oval and has views all the way to the Blue Mountains.
As well as the standard lock up garage there is an additional storage area in the basement car park with double lock up garage, therefore providing secure parking for 3 cars + storage
Other features include; security intercom, resort style pool and one level of visitor parking.
Moments to Westfield shops, trains and premier schools, it will prove a lasting investment.
